author: The Current
description:
Remembering Mike Peters of the Alarm with this 2017 performance at the MPR booth.
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

Back on August 29, 2017, Mike Peters of The Alarm performed live and spoke with host Mark Wheat — all in front of a lively audience at the MPR booth at the Minnesota State Fair.

Video Segments
00:00:00 Mike Peters interview with host Mark Wheat, part 1
00:04:10 Strength
00:07:33 Rain In The Summertime
00:11:12 Interview with host Mark Wheat, part 2
00:13:37 The Stand
00:15:52 Thank-yous and signoff

description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of The Honeydogs, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016.
